Hello,

When HSSFSheet instance is created by 
org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFSheet#createSheet(),instance field 
org.apache.poi.hssf.model.Sheet#marged is(not initialized correctry?) null,
calling HSSFSheet#getNumMergedRegions() and #getMergedRegionAt(int) throws 
NullPointerException.

I found it at 1.8.0dev.

Please try this code.
-------------------------------------------------------------
import org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFSheet;
import org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFWorkbook;

public class POITest {
	public static void main(String args[]){
		HSSFWorkbook b = new HSSFWorkbook();
		HSSFSheet s = b.createSheet();
		System.out.println(s.getNumMergedRegions());
	}
}
